Lesley Baker https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lesley_Baker 0 Lesley Baker (born 20 January 1944) is an Australian actress, singer, dancer and comedian. She was well known for her early appearances on In Melbourne Tonight With Graham Kennedy. After which she went on to play several roles for Crawford Productions series.
